    "description": "<p><strong>BH Builders &amp; Engineering Pte Ltd</strong> was incorporated in 2007 as a private limited company under the laws of Singapore. Our Company is registered with <strong>BCA </strong>under trade <strong>CR03</strong> – <strong>Demolition </strong>and<strong> Workplace Safety Health Council, bizSAFE Star; ISO 45001, ISO 9001 &amp; ISO 14001</strong>. Over the years, we have revolved on mixed construction activities including General Building, Civil Engineering Construction and Rental of Excavators and Breakers and supply recycle concrete aggregate.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our company is engaged in providing specialised and professional services in General Building &amp; Civil Engineering Works.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We have a team of passionate people whom are always striving to provide the most cost effective, timely and quality construction services to our customer. For us, our customers deserved the best.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our success in securing repeated orders from established Clients is testament to our commitment to quality service and total customer satisfaction. We believe a satisfied customer is our greatest gratification for a job well done.</p>",
